questions.scenario:
You are debugging a production issue where a high-throughput payment processing engine starts throwing `java.lang.OutOfMemoryError: Metaspace` after running for several hours in production. The following code snippet is identified as the source of the problem:

java
@Service
public class PaymentProcessingService {
    private final Map<String, PaymentHandler> handlers = new ConcurrentHashMap<>();

    public void process(String providerId, String code) {
        PaymentHandler handler = handlers.computeIfAbsent(providerId, id -> {
            ProxyFactory factory = new ProxyFactory(new DefaultPaymentHandler(code));
            return (PaymentHandler) factory.getProxy(new URLClassLoader(new URL[0], getClass().getClassLoader()));
        });
        handler.handle();
    }
}
